    "description": "Delicious Hollandaise doesn't have to be a risky business. This quick, foolproof method will have you replicating the French classic in no time. We're serving it over buttery cod, crispy, garlicky, crushed potatoes and seasonal greens. Bon app\u00e9tit!",
